{
  "name": "Critical Genius",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/equipment.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may select 1 weapon with which you are proficient (including unarmed strike), treating that weapon as though its critical threat range was 19-20 (unless it would be higher) and its critical multiplier as though it was x2 (even if it would normally be higher). In addition, when you confirm a critical hit with the chosen weapon while using the attack action, you deal additional damage equal to your base attack bonus; this additional damage is applied after other modifiers and is not multiplied by the critical hit. At +10 base attack bonus, the chosen weapon&#8217;s critical threat range is instead treated as 18-20.</p>\n<p><strong>Author's Note:</strong> The change in critical threat range and critical multiplier from this talent is applied before other modifiers, such as the keen weapon property or the weapon mastery class feature.</p>\n",
